title: Am I Invincible
description: [Invincible + Funny + Divine] He always thought he was a mortal, but he didn’t know that his yard was full of divine weapons and the chickens he raised were more like phoenixes! It wasn’t until after five years of living in a mortal village when the system finally allowed him to come into contact with cultivators. It was then that he discovered that no matter how strong someone was, the moment they saw him, they would be so scared that their legs gets numb and call him senior. Some even kneeled down and worshipped him… Am I Invincible I Am Unequalled at What Time When Am I Invincible Wǒ Shénme Shíhòu Wúdíle 我什么时候无敌了
alternative_titles: I Am Unequalled at What Time
